README
------

* script7a.sh: display the script parameters:
  $0: name of the script file that is called
  $#: number of parameters
  $*: parameters as a single value
  $1: value of the second parameter

* script7b.sh: display the script parameters:
  $0: name of the script file that is called
  $#: number of parameters
  $*: parameters as a single value

  use the shift command to shift the parameters to the left

